Suggests: kdebase
Conflicts: koffice (<< 2.1-beta2-1), koffice-common
Description: common libraries and files for the KDE Office Suite
 This package provides the libraries, binaries and other files that are
 shared amongst the various components of KOffice.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE Office Suite.

